=== 特技 ===
[[File:Hercules_met_parachutisten_op_Ginkelse_heide_19_september_2009.jpg|thumb]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/04/08/us/c-130-hercules-military-plane-anniversary/|title=The 'Furious 7' plane that just won't quit|author=Thom Patterson|publisher=''[[CNN|CNN]]''|date=2015-04-08|accessdate=2015-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413085751/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/04/08/us/c-130-hercules-military-plane-anniversary|archive-date=2015-04-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>负责将车子从[[索诺兰沙漠|索诺兰沙漠]]上方1.2万英尺高的天空中扔下，使到汽车掉落的速度介于130-140英里/每小时之间<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nypost.com/2015/03/30/how-furious-7-filmmakers-pushed-5-cars-out-a-plane-at-12000-feet/|title=<nowiki>How ‘Furious 7’ filmmakers pushed 5 cars out a plane at 12,000 feet</nowiki>|author=Reed Tucker|publisher=''[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]''|date=2015-03-30|accessdate=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402191238/http://nypost.com/2015/03/30/how-furious-7-filmmakers-pushed-5-cars-out-a-plane-at-12000-feet/|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://au.ibtimes.com/furious-7-stunt-coordinators-crew-members-speak-about-air-drop-scene-movie-1429693|title='Furious 7' Stunt Coordinators And Crew Members Speak About The Air Drop Scene In The Movie|author=Sachin Trivedi|publisher=''[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]''|date=2015-03-16|accessdate=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418112706/http://au.ibtimes.com/furious-7-stunt-coordinators-crew-members-speak-about-air-drop-scene-movie-1429693|archive-date=2015-04-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>]]
构思“空投”场景的特技协调员斯皮罗·拉扎托斯（Spiro Razatos），曾在[[速度与激情5|第五部]]和[[速度与激情6|第六部]]的剧组工作<ref name="BI"/><ref name="USA"/>。拉扎托斯告诉《[[商业内幕|商业内幕]]》杂志，他想更多地依靠货真价实的特技，而不用[[CGI|CGI]]，好让整个场景“充满真实感”，回应观众的期待<ref name="BI">{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.in/How-Furious-7-dropped-real-cars-from-planes-in-its-most-ridiculous-stunt-yet/articleshow/46790017.cms|title=How 'Furious 7' dropped real cars from planes in its most ridiculous stunt yet|author=Jason Guerrasio|publisher=''[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]''|date=2015-04-03|accessdate=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403163933/http://www.businessinsider.in/How-Furious-7-dropped-real-cars-from-planes-in-its-most-ridiculous-stunt-yet/articleshow/46790017.cms|archive-date=2015-04-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该特技需耗费数月来解决难题。摄影机需要安装在车子里，以便汽车着陆时不被损坏，为此剧组得想出让汽车扔出飞机的安全方式。他们先试着将单辆汽车扔出飞机<ref name="BI"/>，这个测试重复了六次之多<ref name="USA"/>。车子由[[C-130运输机|C-130运输机]]运至[[索诺兰沙漠|索诺兰沙漠]]上空，落在科罗拉多州的山路上<ref name="USA">{{cite web|url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2015/04/secrets-behind-the-three-most-amazing-stunts-in-furious-7|title=The secrets behind the three most amazing stunts in 'Furious 7'|author=Hamel Jhavera|publisher=''[[USA_Today|USA Today]]''|date=2015-04-03|accessdate=2015-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406015724/http://ftw.usatoday.com/2015/04/secrets-behind-the-three-most-amazing-stunts-in-furious-7|archive-date=2015-04-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两架飞机于1.2万英尺的高度飞行<ref name="BI"/>，每次投放两辆车，车上的[[弹道补救系统|弹道补救系统]]降落伞在空投前启用[[GPS|GPS]]功能。大约到了五千英尺时部署降落伞<ref name="USA"/>。拍摄该场景用了十个攝影機，其中除了地面的攝影機，还有在飞机内远程操作的攝影機，另有三个安装在车子内。额外的攝影機在直升机上，拉扎托斯用它来监视。三名跳伞员戴上有攝影機的头盔，从多个角度协助镜头的拍摄。跳伞员或跟着汽车跳出，还是紧随其后。虽然所有的车子降落在空投区，但有30%的车子没能在预定地点降落<ref name="USA"/>。至于要展现车子里的表演的特写镜头，每辆车要装上360度全域运动的大型万向架，还要克服绿幕的缺点，重现他们在天空中翻滚的状态<ref name="OCR">{{cite web|url=http://m.ocregister.com/articles/car-656462-cars-furious.html|title=Reel deal steel|author=Susan Carpenter|publisher=''[[Orange_County_Register|Orange County Register]]''|accessdate=2015-04-10}}{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。车子上路的最后一部分场景则是单独拍摄的。为了获得该项权利，剧组用滑轮系统让车子与地面相隔六到十英尺以上。当车子由起重机吊下时，特技演员坐在驾驶座将引擎发动至每小时35到40英尺，全速滑向地面。这些起重机在后期被删掉<ref name="USA"/><ref name="OCR"/>。拉扎托斯承认，空投场景完全真实也“难到极点”<ref name="BI"/><ref name="USA"/>。

保罗·沃克饰演的布莱恩从坠落山崖的公交车中跳上悬崖的场景，则由替身演员完成，也没有任何的电脑特效<ref name="S2">{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.in/One-of-the-most-insane-stunts-in-Furious-7-almost-didnt-happen/articleshow/46818645.cms|title=One of the most insane stunts in 'Furious 7' almost didn't happen|author=Jason Guerrasio|publisher=''[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]''|date=2015-04-06|accessdate=2015-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408042242/http://www.businessinsider.in/One-of-the-most-insane-stunts-in-Furious-7-almost-didnt-happen/articleshow/46818645.cms|archive-date=2015-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该场景原定与唐老大一行人试图援助拉姆齐的场景一同拍摄，但后来因科罗拉多州没有税收减免而中断<ref name="S2"/>。工作室原本想在能为电影制作减税的乔治亚州拍摄该场景，然后后期将树林加到背景中，但被拉扎托斯否决：“观众会看出来（它是CGI）的，这样对表演就没有好感了<ref name="S2"/>。”拍摄最终在科罗拉多州进行<ref name="S2"/>。

共有340辆汽车在片中亮相<ref name="OCR"/>，超过230辆车在拍攝过程中被损毁，其中不乏[[梅赛德斯-奔驰|梅赛德斯-奔驰]]、[[三菱帕杰罗|三菱帕杰罗]]和[[福德皇冠维多利亚|福德皇冠维多利亚]]<ref name="WSJ">{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/furious-7-what-happened-to-the-wrecked-cars-1427907293|title=<nowiki>‘Furious 7’: What Happened to the Wrecked Cars</nowiki>|author=Steve Knopper|publisher=''[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]''|date=2015-04-01|accessdate=2015-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150410003127/http://www.wsj.com/articles/furious-7-what-happened-to-the-wrecked-cars-1427907293|archive-date=2015-04-10|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。在科罗拉多州国君栈道（Monarch Pass）高速公路拍摄的场景，有超过40辆车被毁，是全片最具破坏性的场景<ref name="WSJ"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/furious-7-230-cars-were-787486|title='Furious 7': Over 230 Cars Were Destroyed During Film's Shoot|author=Ryan Gajewski|publisher=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]''|date=2015-04-09|accessdate=2015-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412014613/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/furious-7-230-cars-were-787486|archive-date=2015-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。全片仅有10%的动作场景由電腦生成，大部分CGI只是简单地删掉真正的汽车和赛车手，或是对背景的修饰<ref name="OCR"/>。完成电影的各种特技用了超过3500个人工作日(man-days)<ref name="OCR"/>。出于安全考虑，特技协调员乔尔·克莱默（Joel Kramer）表示他不会让司机开到每小时50英里<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3033091/Actress-publicly-said-female-stunt-driver-Furious-7-unmasked-FRAUD-extra-set.html|title=Fast & furious fraud! Actress who claimed she was the 'only female stunt driver in Furious 7' and even photoshopped herself into movie poster was just an extra|author=Snejana Farberov|publisher=''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]''|date=2015-04-10|accessdate=2015-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411024719/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3033091/Actress-publicly-said-female-stunt-driver-Furious-7-unmasked-FRAUD-extra-set.html|archive-date=2015-04-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 保羅·沃克的角色重置 ===
2014年1月6日，據報導，沃克的角色將以退休的方式離開電影，並非他殺<ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.time.com/2014/01/06/heres-what-will-happen-to-paul-walkers-character-in-fast-and-furious-7/|title=Paul Walker's Fast and Furious Fate: How The Movie Will Deal With His Death|last=Stampler|first=Laura|work=Time.com|date=2014-01-06|accessdate=2014-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110150856/http://entertainment.time.com/2014/01/06/heres-what-will-happen-to-paul-walkers-character-in-fast-and-furious-7/|archive-date=2014-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，作家克里斯·摩根拒絕討論決定，或者採用其他方式都仍在考慮<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/14/decision-on-paul-walkers-character-in-fast-and-furious-7-not-made-yet|title=A Decision on Paul Walker's Character in Fast and Furious 7 Has Not Been Made Yet|last=Cornet|first=Roth|work=IGN.com|date=2014-01-13|accessdate=2014-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223231112/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/14/decision-on-paul-walkers-character-in-fast-and-furious-7-not-made-yet|archive-date=2014-02-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年3月21日，每日新聞報導，工作室已聘請四名與沃克長得很像演員來輔助，並以[[電腦成像|電腦成像]]的方式來構成保羅的體魄、臉和聲音<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/confidential/fast-furious-7-double-time-walker-article-1.1728704|title='Fast & Furious 7' will shoot scenes with doubles and replace Paul Walker with CGI to keep him in the film|last=Garvey|first=Marianne|last2=Niemietz|first2=Brian|last3=Cartwright|first3=Lachlan|work=The New York Daily News|date=2014-03-21|accessdate=2014-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321094942/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/confidential/fast-furious-7-double-time-walker-article-1.1728704|archive-date=2014-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年4月15日宣布由沃克的弟弟[[卡萊·沃克|卡萊]]（Caleb）和[[科迪·沃克|科迪]]（Cody）擔任他的替身<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/paul-walker-brothers-fast-furious-7-filming-help/|title=Paul Walker's Brothers Jumping In To Help Finish 'Fast & Furious 7' Action Scenes|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2014-04-15|accessdate=2014-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418134956/http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/paul-walker-brothers-fast-furious-7-filming-help/|archive-date=2014-04-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，科迪更因此踏足演藝圈。为了重现沃克的面容和躯体，剧组特别聘请[[彼得·杰克逊|彼得·杰克逊]]的[[维塔数码|维塔数码]]。成片包含CGI和精心挑选用在沃克兄弟身上的摄像机角度及灯光的合成镜头，用以模仿沃克的外型<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/heres-how-paul-walker-completed-his-unfinished-scenes-in-furious-7_-231586.html|title=Here's How Paul Walker Completed His Unfinished Scenes In Furious 7|author=Rishab Banerji|work=[[The_Times_of_India|India Times]]|date=2015-04-04|accessdate=2015-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404154728/http://www.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/heres-how-paul-walker-completed-his-unfinished-scenes-in-furious-7_-231586.html|archive-date=2015-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伦敦特效工作室The Mill的CEO罗宾·申菲尔德（Robin Shenfield）指出，本次重建与在拍摄《[[角斗士_(电影)|角斗士]]》的过程中去世的[[奥利弗·里德|奥利弗·里德]]相同<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/furious-7-how-peter-jacksons-784157|title='Furious 7' and How Peter Jackson's Weta Created Digital Paul Walker|author=Carolyn Giardina|publisher=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]''|date=2015-03-25|accessdate=2015-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414195830/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/furious-7-how-peter-jacksons-784157|archive-date=2015-04-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

