2015年3月27日，電影與[[微软|微软]]旗下竞速游戏《[[極限競速：地平線2|極限競速：地平線2]]》推出名為《Forza Horizon 2 Presents Fast & Furious》的獨立擴充包<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-02-25-forza-horizon-2-presents-fast-and-furious-is-a-standalone-expansion|title=Forza Horizon 2 Presents Fast & Furious is a standalone expansion|author=Wesley Yin-Poole|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2015-02-25|accessdate=2015-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328072609/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-02-25-forza-horizon-2-presents-fast-and-furious-is-a-standalone-expansion|archive-date=2015-03-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

